    },
    {
        "text": "(thunder rumbles)",
        "start": 10.24,
        "duration": 2.833
    },
    {
        "text": "- Hurricane Maria hit us hard.",
        "start": 21.46,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Our solar panels and house survived,",
        "start": 23.62,
        "duration": 2.51
    },
    {
        "text": "but the whole system collapsed.",
        "start": 26.13,
        "duration": 2.27
    },
    {
        "text": "I needed cash, but the banks were closed,",
        "start": 28.4,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "and credit cards were just plastic.",
        "start": 30.65,
        "duration": 1.825
    },
    {
        "text": "(bright music)",
        "start": 32.475,
        "duration": 2.045
    },
    {
        "text": "A friend in Missouri told me,",
        "start": 34.52,
        "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Why don't I send you money\nthrough Western Union?\"",
        "start": 36.1,
        "duration": 2.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Shortly after the devastation\nfrom Hurricane Maria,",
        "start": 38.69,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "Western Union sent a plane\nof cash to Puerto Rico.",
        "start": 41.66,
        "duration": 3.399
    },
    {
        "text": "Gracias.",
        "start": 45.059,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Now I could begin helping my neighbors.",
        "start": 45.892,
        "duration": 2.391
    },
    {
        "text": "There will be other other storms,",
        "start": 53.9,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "but we'll be ready to\nweather them, together.",
        "start": 55.56,
        "duration": 2.48
    }
]